== 制作 ==
[[File:Rick_Baker_February_2015_(cropped).jpg|upright]]采用特效化妆制作《恐怖食肉虫》的特效]]

杰夫·利伯曼为《恐怖食肉虫》编剧时正参与[[雅努斯影业|雅努斯影业]]（{{lang|en|Janus Films}}）项目《电影艺术》（{{lang|en|''The Art of Film''}}），他在项目工作结束后构想本片应对工作压力<ref name="Fangoria1993">{{cite magazine | magazine = Fangoria | title = The Squirm Turns | last = Szulkin | first = David | pages = 24–29 | date = 1993-06 | issue = 123 | url = https://archive.org/details/Fangoria_123_1993_Ticks_DaveWooderson-DREGS_c2c}}</ref>。利伯曼小时候曾看到哥哥用[[变压器|变压器]]给泥土通电迫使地里的蠕虫钻出来，抓这些虫子去钓鱼，把他“吓得屁滚尿流”<ref name="Fangoria1993" />。他还听说印第安纳州[[弗洛伊茲諾布斯_(印地安納州)|弗洛伊茲諾布斯]]发生[[倍足綱|千足虫]]入侵民居<ref name="Starlog">{{cite magazine | magazine = Starlog | title = Squirm | last = O'Quinn | first = Kerry | issue = 1 | date = 1976-08 | pages = 20–21 | url = https://archive.org/details/starlog_magazine-001/page/n19/mode/2up | access-date = 2020-12-12}}</ref>，此外，1963年恐怖片《[[鳥_(電影)|群鸟]]》也是他创作本片的灵感来源<ref name="DVDTalk2">{{cite web | url = https://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/65274/squirm/ | title = Squirm (Blu-ray) | last = Dahlke | first = Kurt | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200603201501/https://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/65274/squirm/ | work = DVD Talk | date = 2014-10-28 | accessdate = 2020-12-12 | archive-date = 2020-06-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

利伯曼用六周写完初稿，制片人乔治·马内西（{{lang|en|George Manasse}}）觉得很有潜力并向[[百老匯劇院|百老汇]]独立制作人埃德加·兰斯伯里（{{lang|en|Edgar Lansbury}}）和约瑟夫·贝鲁（{{lang|en|Joseph Beruh}}）推荐。两从在1975年夏季看过后买断剧本，并自掏47万美元投入项目。《恐怖食肉虫》随后成为蠕虫公司制作的唯一一部电影。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b972f3a44 | title = The Squirm Company | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200720054142/https://www.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b972f3a44 | work = [[英國電影協會|British Film Institute]] | access-date = 2020-12-12 | archive-date = 2020-07-20 | dead-url = no}}</ref>影片情节起初定在[[新英格蘭|新英格蘭]]并计划实地取景<ref name="Fangoria1993" />，但因美国东北部秋季天气不适合拍摄改在乔治亚州[[溫特沃斯港_(喬治亞州)|溫特沃斯港]]摄制<ref name="Muir-2012">{{cite book | last = Muir | first = John | title = Horror Films of the 1970s | date = 2012-11-22 | publisher = McFarland & Company | isbn = 978-0-7864-9156-8}}</ref>{{rp|18}}<ref name="Fangoria1993" />。1975年11月，电影在温暖的乔治亚州开拍<ref name="Fangoria1993" />。

[[金·貝辛格|金·貝辛格]]曾参与杰里一角试镜，但利伯曼看不上，觉得观众不会相信她这样的姑娘会在片中那种乡下小镇生活。后来利伯曼对此非常后悔，自认当时真是白痴。[[馬田·辛|马丁·辛]]本已入选扮演米克，后来被斯卡尔蒂诺取代。马丁·辛建议米克的职业背景是演员，而且设想他是在背诵《[[哈姆雷特|哈姆雷特]]》选段时发现亚伦·比兹利的骨架。<ref name="Fangoria1993" />简·沙利文因在[[田纳西·威廉斯|田纳西·威廉斯]]剧作中的南方口音获选扮演杰里之母娜奥米<ref name="DVDTalk2" />。为演好罗杰，R·A·道前往溫特沃斯港花费数周训练[[方法演技|方法演技]]<ref name="DVDTalk2" />。

电影拍摄期间使用的蠕虫有一半是用橡胶制作，其他的许多都是缅因州大型沙虫，冷藏后运到溫特沃斯港<ref name="Fangoria1993" />，另有[[斯基达韦海洋学研究所|乔治亚大学海洋学研究所]]提供的约300万条红虫<ref name="AFI" />。为让蠕虫动起来，下方铺有电线并通电<ref name="Fangoria1993" />。为拍摄客厅满是蠕虫的镜头，剧组搭建1.2米的脚手架，上面盖着帆布，再在帆布上铺着厚15厘米、数以万计的蠕虫。剧组聘请当地[[美國童軍|童子军]]从下方挪动帆布，令蠕虫看起来不断起伏，这些童子军为此获[[优异奖章_(美国童军)|优异奖章]]。<ref name="Fangoria1993" /><ref name="BoxOffice1">{{cite magazine | magazine = Box Office | title = Horror-Thriller 'Squirm' Completed in Georgia | date = 1976-01-12 | page = 14 | access-date = 2020-12-13 | archive-date = 2020-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200710222710/http://www2.boxoffice.com/the_vault/issue_page?issue_id=1976-1-12&page_no=14 | url = http://www2.boxoffice.com/the_vault/issue_page?issue_id=1976-1-12&page_no=14 | dead-url = no}}</ref>电影制作收尾后，缅因州报纸宣称该州渔业受到本片制作的不利影响<ref name="Fangoria1993" />。

布莱恩·斯梅德利-阿斯顿（{{lang|en|Brian Smedley-Aston}}）担任本片剪辑师<ref>{{cite magazine | magazine = Shivers | title = Expose | last = Lynn | first = France | issue = 3 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/Shivers_03/page/n18/mode/2up 19]–21 | date = 1992-10 | access-date = 2020-12-13 | url = https://archive.org/details/Shivers_03}}</ref>，罗伯特·普林斯（{{lang|en|Robert Prince}}）谱写配乐并在英格兰指挥乐队演奏。曾为《[[地球停转之日|地球停转之日]]》（1951年）和《[[驚魂記|驚魂記]]》（1960年）作曲的[[伯纳德·赫尔曼|伯纳德·赫尔曼]]原定参与本片制作，但在投入工作前去世。<ref name="Starlog" />约瑟夫·曼吉恩（{{lang|en|Joseph Mangine}}）担任[[攝影指導|摄影总监]]，亨利·施拉迪（{{lang|en|Henry Shrady}}）任[[藝術總監|藝術總監]]<ref name="BoxOffice1" />。[[特效化妆|特效化妆]]师[[里克·贝克|里克·贝克]]在纽约完成罗杰一角的化妆，把R·A·道变成“蠕虫脸”。这是贝克首次应用特效化妆技术，他先制作面部模具，用[[单丝渔线|单丝渔线]]把覆盖润滑剂的假蠕虫从面部皮肤上拉出来。<ref name="Fangoria1993" />

[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]耗时五周，其中一周用于处理蠕虫。利伯曼在[[後期製作|後期製作]]投入大量心力，使用气球和剪刀制作蠕虫音效，再用[[多轨录音|多轨录音]]将两种声音循环。蠕虫牙齿的声音用剪刀开合模拟，蠕虫尖叫声取自[[布赖恩·德帕尔马|布赖恩·德帕尔马]]1976年电影《[[凶靈|魔女嘉莉]]》的杀猪桥段。<ref name="Fangoria1993" />

== 发行 ==
《恐怖食肉虫》在1976年5月[[第29屆坎城影展|戛纳电影节]]播映后由[[美国国际影业|美国国际影业]]买断发行权，同年7月14日在美国院线上映，8月9日扩大到全球放映<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="BoxOffice2">{{cite magazine | magazine = Box Office | title = AIP Arranges July Release of Terror Drama 'Squirm' | date = 1976-07-19 | page = 5 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200712023132/http://www2.boxoffice.com/the_vault/issue_page?issue_id=1976-7-19&page_no=5 | url = http://www2.boxoffice.com/the_vault/issue_page?issue_id=1976-7-19&page_no=5 | archive-date = 2020-07-12}}</ref>。美国国际影业先向制片人预付25万美元购买国内发行权，另外50万美元承诺至少在16个国家和地区放映<ref name="AFI" />。

美国国际影业希望[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]能为本片[[美国电影分级制度|评级]]“PG”，但协会认为片中绝大多数恐怖场面都不符合PG级标准<ref name="Fangoria1993" />。电影为此剪掉大部分恐怖镜头和帕特里夏·皮尔西洗澡的桥段，电影时长因此缩短一分钟，但92分钟的新版本最后依然是“R”级<ref name="DVDTalk" /><ref name="Fangoria1993" />。在电视上播放时剪掉的内容更多，导演对此表示：电影版的蠕虫攻击至少还能把故事讲通，电视版的剪法简直荒谬<ref name="Fangoria1993" />。电影商业上颇为成功，兰斯伯里和贝鲁单靠海外电影市场就足以收回投资<ref name="Fangoria1993" />。

1983年，[[维斯特朗视频|维斯特朗视频]]发行本片[[家用录像系统|VHS]]录像带<ref name="Fangoria1983">{{cite magazine | magazine = Fangoria | title = The Video Eye of Dr. Cyclops | author = Dr. Cyclops | issue = 29 | date = 1983-09 | page = [https://archive.org/details/Fangoria_029_c2c_1983_Gates_of_Hell_Sproutcore-Bollywox-DREGS/page/n29/mode/2up 27] | url = https://archive.org/details/Fangoria_029_c2c_1983_Gates_of_Hell_Sproutcore-Bollywox-DREGS | access-date = 2020-12-13}}</ref>，2003年[[米高梅家用娱乐|米高梅家用娱乐]]发布[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]。DVD版长93分钟，恢复剪掉的淋浴片段并有包括导演[[评论音轨|评论音轨]]在内的特别花絮<ref name="DVDTalk" />。2011年，米高梅家用娱乐将本片与《[[沼泽怪物|沼泽怪物]]》（{{lang|en|''Swamp Thing''}}，1982年）、《[[活死人归来|活死人归来]]》（''{{lang|en|The Return of the Living Dead}}''，1985年）一起发行套装<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.allmovie.com/movie/squirm-v46341/releases | title = Squirm – Releases | work = [[AllMovie|AllMovie]] | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-date = 2019-04-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190407220725/https://www.allmovie.com/movie/squirm-v46341/releases}}</ref>。2013年9月23日，[[箭牌影业|箭牌视频]]在英国发行本片未剪辑版[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]和DVD<ref name="JoBlo">{{cite web | url = https://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/jeff-liebermanns-cult-classic-squirm-hitting-uk-blu-ray-dvd-september-23 | title = Jeff Lieberman's cult classic Squirm hitting UK Blu-Ray & DVD September 23 | website = JoBlo.com | date = 2013-09-04 | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-date = 2020-06-03 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200603023849/https://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/jeff-liebermanns-cult-classic-squirm-hitting-uk-blu-ray-dvd-september-23}}</ref>。2014年10月28日，[[呐喊工厂|呐喊工厂]]（{{lang|en|Shout! Factory}}）在美国发行未剪辑版蓝光光碟<ref name="Bloody">{{cite web | url = https://bloody-disgusting.com/home-video/3310212/scream-factory-will-make-squirm-halloween/ | title = Scream Factory! Will Make You 'Squirm' This Halloween | last = Miska | first = Brad | work = Bloody Disgusting | date = 2014-08-26 | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190808041304/https://bloody-disgusting.com/home-video/3310212/scream-factory-will-make-squirm-halloween/ | archive-date = 2019-08-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。此外，《恐怖食肉虫》还在[[亞馬遜影片|亞馬遜影片]]、[[Tubi|Tubi]]和[[战栗_(流媒体服务)|战栗]]（{{lang|en|Shudder}}）提供[[流媒体|流媒体]]观看<ref name="TV">{{cite web | url = https://www.tvguide.com/movies/squirm/review/118818/ | title = Squirm Review | work = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190807042231/https://www.tvguide.com/movies/squirm/review/118818/ | archive-date = 2019-08-07 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/the-best-horror-movies-to-watch-on-shudder/ | title = Best Horror Movies to Watch on Shudder Right Now | last1 = Fletcher | first1 = Rosie | last2 = Kaye | first2 = Don | work = Den of Geek | date = 2020-09-26 | access-date = 2020-12-13 | archive-date = 2020-10-22 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201022071705/https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/the-best-horror-movies-to-watch-on-shudder/}}</ref>。

=== 评价 ===
[[File:Squirm_Wormface.jpg|thumb]]

影评人普遍认可电影的特效和恐怖元素，许多评论称赞片中特效令人毛骨悚然<ref name="Allmovie">{{cite web | url = https://www.allmovie.com/movie/squirm-v46341/review | title = Squirm (1976) | last = Guarisco | first = Donald | work = Allmovie | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190407220724/https://www.allmovie.com/movie/squirm-v46341/review | archive-date = 2019-04-07 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Craig-2019">{{cite book | last = Craig | first = Rob | title = American International Pictures: A Comprehensive Filmography | date = 2019 | publisher = [[麥克法蘭公司出版社|McFarland & Company]] | isbn = 978-1-4766-6631-0 | page = [https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=e0CIDwAAQBAJ&lpg=PA78&pg=PA349&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false 349]}}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{cite journal | date = 1976-08-11 | title = Squirm | access-date = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200607204540/https://variety.com/1975/film/reviews/squirm-1200423655/ | dead-url = no | url = https://variety.com/1975/film/reviews/squirm-1200423655/ | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archive-date = 2020-06-07 | page = 19}}</ref>。《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》认为蠕虫桥段“实在可怕”<ref name= "TV" />，《[[神奇影院|神奇影院]]》（''{{lang|en|Cinefantastique}}''）刊登卡尔·康茨（{{lang|en|Kyle B. Counts}}）的评论，称蠕虫钻进罗杰面部的过程“熟练到可怕”<ref name="Cinefantastique">{{cite magazine | magazine = Cinefantastique | title = Film Ratings | last = Counts | first = Kyle | volume = 5 | number = 3 | date = Winter 1976 | page = 29 | access-date = 2020-12-13 | url = https://archive.org/stream/cinefantastique_1970-2002/Cinefantastique%20Vol%2005%20No%203%20%281976%29#page/n27/mode/2up}}</ref>。[[文森特·坎比|文森特·坎比]]（{{lang|en|Vincent Canby}}）在《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》发文，觉得蠕虫桥段“令人特别反胃”，他很不喜欢罗杰掉进大堆蠕虫的镜头，感觉就像肉酱投入意大利面<ref name="NYT">{{cite news | last = Canby | first = Vincent | date = 1975-12-31 | title = The Screen:'Squirm' Shows Worms Turning on People | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1976/07/31/archives/the-screensquirm-shows-worms-turning-on-people.html | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | page = 8 | access-date = 2020-12-13 | archive-date = 2019-08-06 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190806051209/https://www.nytimes.com/1976/07/31/archives/the-screensquirm-shows-worms-turning-on-people.html}}</ref>。罗布·克雷格（{{lang|en|Rob Craig}}）2019年著作《美国国际影业》同样认为本片恐怖之处就于在血淋淋的特效化妆<ref name="Craig-2019" />，他还称赞电影用蠕虫这样本来毫无威胁的动物传达出恐惧感，将它们“堆积成庞大的群体，形成有意识的杀人武器”<ref name="Craig-2019" />。2013年版《[[伦纳德·马尔丁电影指南|伦纳德·马尔丁电影指南]]》（''{{lang|en|Leonard Maltin's Movie Guide}}''）认为《恐怖食肉虫》在恐怖片中表现高于平均水平，恐怖桥段层层递进，效果良好<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Maltin | first1 = Leonard | last2 = Carson | first2 = Darwyn | title = Leonard Maltin's Movie Guide: The Modern Era | year = 2013 | page = [https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780451418104/page/1318/mode/2up 1318] | publisher = Signet | isbn = 978-0-451-41810-4}}</ref>。唐纳德·瓜里斯科（{{lang|en|Donald Guarisco}}）在[[AllMovie|AllMovie]]发文，称赞罗伯特·普林斯作曲时对[[合成器|合成器]]的应用“令人坐立不安”<ref name="Allmovie" />。

影评人对演员表演和电影制作反响不佳，对导演评价不一<ref name="Cinefantastique" /><ref name="LA Times" /><ref name="Bulletin">{{cite journal | last = Pym | first = John | date = 1976-09 | title = Squirm | journal = The Monthly Film Bulletin | volume = 43 | issue = 512 | page = 199}}</ref>凯文·托马斯（{{lang|en|Kevin Thomas}}）在《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》发文，认可利伯曼在情节平衡上的处理，在危机迅速升级同时巧妙展示毫无威胁感的民间气氛<ref name="LA Times">{{cite news | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | title = As the Worm Turns: 'Squirm' | last = Thomas | first = Kevin | date = 1976-12-17 | page = 21 | via = Newspapers.com | quote = "Squirm" (citywide) is guaranteed to make you do just that. Made on location in Georgia, it's a nifty little horror picture that strikes a good balance between humor and terror. While not morbid, it is nevertheless graphic enough to place it out of bounds for the faint-hearted and for impressionable youngsters.}}</ref>。《电视指南》认为本片“就像利伯曼大部分作品一样”未获应得的认可<ref name="TV" />。康茨批评导演对毛骨悚然桥段的处理“笨手笨脚”，效果大打折扣<ref name="Cinefantastique" />；《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》杂志也觉得电影制作“笨拙且业余”，削弱特效的恐怖感<ref name="Variety" />。影评人认可电影摄影<ref name="Allmovie" /><ref name="Craddock-2006">{{cite book | last = Craddock | first = Jim | title = VideoHound's Golden Movie Retriever | year = 2006 | publisher = Gale Group | isbn = 0-7876-8980-7 | page = [https://archive.org/details/videohoundsgolde2006crad/page/808/mode/2up 809]}}</ref>。[[约翰·肯尼斯·缪尔|约翰·肯尼斯·缪尔]]（{{lang|en|John Kenneth Muir}}）称赞电影制作和画面，但令人失望的地方在于前后意境不一，而且没有真实可信的人物<ref name="Muir-2012" />{{rp|134–136}}。坎比认为斯卡尔蒂诺和皮尔西的演出还不赖<ref name="NYT" />。

《恐怖食肉虫》上映后《综艺》和《纽约时报》观感一般<ref name="Variety" /><ref name="NYT" />，但随着时间的推迟，电影评价逐渐好转。康茨的评价认为电影老是从暴力镜头切换到搞笑场面，导致电影气氛上不去<ref name="Cinefantastique" />，但托马斯觉得影片对幽默和恐怖的平衡把握出色<ref name="LA Times" />。约翰·皮姆（{{lang|en|John Pym}}）在《[[电影月报|电影月报]]》（''{{lang|en|The Monthly Film Bulletin}}''）发文，称电影的恐怖和渲染值得称道<ref name="Bulletin" />。瓜里斯科认为本片堪称“大自然复仇恐怖片”的典范之作，称赞电影的第三幕令观众投入情节，关注人物命运<ref name="Allmovie" />。多年后，许多媒体在回顾时认可本片表现，《恐怖食肉虫》成为[[邪典追捧|邪典经典]]<ref name="JoBlo" /><ref name="Bloody" /><ref name="Time" />，片中幽默和主题赢得认可<ref name="TV" /><ref name="Time" />。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》于2010年将本片列入“十佳杀手动物电影”，称赞片中部分镜头就像《惊魂记》浴室杀人桥段的“病态扭曲”<ref name="Time">{{cite journal | page = 6 | archive-date = 2019-12-23 | url = https://entertainment.time.com/2010/08/20/top-10-killer-animal-movies/slide/squirm/ | title = Top 10 Killer-Animal Movies | last = Abbott | first = Kate | journal = [[時代雜誌|Time]] | date = 2010-08-19 | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191223075517/http://entertainment.time.com/2010/08/20/top-10-killer-animal-movies/slide/squirm/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《电视指南》发文称赞片中无论幽默还是恐怖桥段都颇具“假正经”风味，致敬《惊魂记》的场景也不例外<ref name="TV" />。克雷格认为影片娱乐效果和眼光都值得称道，相比之下演员表现颇有不及<ref name="Craig-2019" />。吉姆·克拉多克（{{lang|en|Jim Craddock}}）的著作《金牌电影检索》称《恐怖食肉虫》表现还过得去，是“还好”的巨型蠕虫电影<ref name="Craddock-2006" />。

== 分析 ==
《恐怖食肉虫》可以视为“大自然复仇”电影，是20世纪70年代初由《[[毒蛙_(电影)|毒蛙]]》（''{{lang|en|Frogs}}''）、《[[魔兔之夜|魔兔之夜]]》（''{{lang|en|Night of the Lepus}}''）催生的电影类型<ref name="Verevis-2016">{{cite book | last = Verevis | first = Constantine | chapter = Vicious cycle: ''Jaws'' and the revenge-of-nature films of the 1970s | editor1 = Amanda Ann Klein | editor2 = R. Barton Palmer | title = Cycles, Sequels, Spin-offs, Remakes, and Reboots: Multiplicities in Film and Television | page = [https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=IvK4CwAAQBAJ&pg=PA102&redir_esc=y 102] | date = 2016-03-15 | publisher = University of Texas Press | isbn = 978-1-4773-0817-2}}</ref><ref name="Platts-2015">{{cite book | last = Platts | first = Todd | year = 2015 | chapter = The New Horror Movie | editor1-last = Cogan | editor1-first = Brian | editor2-last = Gencarelli | editor2-first = Thom | title = Baby Boomers and Popular Culture | publisher = [[格林伍德出版集團|Praeger]] | pages = 156–157}}</ref>。《[[大白鯊_(電影)|大白鲨]]》是该类型片的代表作<ref name="Verevis-2016" /><ref name="Platts-2015" />，此后各种续集或类似取材的电影层出不穷，想借前作的巨大成功从市场分一杯羹。但[[电影研究|电影研究]]学者亨特（{{lang|en|I.Q. Hunter}}）指出，[[昆汀·塔伦蒂诺|昆汀·塔伦蒂诺]]曾将20世纪70年代初的这种类型片称为“大自然母亲发狂片”，《大白鲨》不过是这种潮流的延续<ref>{{cite book | author = I.Q. Hunter | title = Cult Film as a Guide to Life: Fandom, Adaptation, and Identity | date = 2016-09-08 | publisher = Bloomsbury Publishing | page = [https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=KaqaDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA85&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false 85] | isbn = 978-1-62356-381-3}}</ref>。缪尔将这种类型称为“生态恐怖片”，“这些电影反映观众对大自然母亲不会容忍人类掠夺和污染地球的真实恐惧”<ref name="Muir-2012" />{{rp|2}}。

影评人[[罗宾·伍德|罗宾·伍德]]（{{lang|en|Robin Wood}}）认为恐怖片反映的是性压抑和家庭关系紧张问题，《恐怖食肉虫》就是“大自然母亲复仇”的代表作，觉得片尾不应该有三个主要人物幸存，因为蠕虫体现的电影逻辑是大自然力量不可阻挡，三人幸存不符上述逻辑<ref>{{cite book | last = Wood | first = Robin | year = 2018 | title = Robin Wood on the Horror Film: Collected Essays and Reviews | chapter = Return of the Repressed | publisher = Wayne State University Press | isbn = 978-0-8143-4524-5}}</ref>。罗布·克雷格指出，片中描绘的乡村居民“愚昧无知、各行其事、保守反动、腐败无能，甚至有可能是疯子”，蠕虫可以视为隐喻，意指“乡巴佬软弱且粘糊糊的生殖器，单独来看既可笑又脆弱，但联合起来却非常危险”，反过来喻示乡下人虽然就像“乱七八糟的面条”，但依然是危险的社会力量<ref name="Craig-2019" />。康茨声称，本片与《[[稻草狗|稻草狗]]》（''{{lang|en|Straw Dogs}}''）都有类似的“男子理想”主题，男主角便是英雄，但他也认为，《恐怖食肉虫》不会让人觉得米克最后成长为“真正的男人”<ref name="Cinefantastique" />。

利伯曼为乔恩·陶森（{{lang|en|Jon Towlson}}）2014年著作《颠覆恐怖电影：科学怪人至今电影蕴含的反文化信息》（{{lang|en|''Subversive Horror Cinema: Countercultural Messages of Films from Frankenstein to the Present''}}）作序，文中针对《恐怖食肉虫》引发的批判和学术分析表示：

