== 影响 ==
导演布赖恩·德帕尔马1981年的电影《[[凶线|凶线]]》多个镜头出现《恐怖食肉虫》电影海报。利伯曼是德帕尔马的影迷，他在接受《[[疯哥利牙|疯哥利牙]]》（''{{lang|en|Fangoria}}''）采访时自称曾在多年后向德帕尔马问起此事，德帕尔马回答“只用最好的！”<ref name="Fangoria1993" />音乐家[[怪人保罗·佩特罗斯基|怪人保罗·佩特罗斯基]]（{{lang|en|"Weird Paul" Petroskey}}）创作专辑《鸡蛋奶油里的蠕虫》（{{lang|en|''Worm in My Egg Cream''}}），意指《恐怖食肉虫》中米克点的鸡蛋奶油里居然有蠕虫。专辑由佩特罗斯基旗下石滚唱片（{{lang|en|Rocks & Rolling Records}}）发行，<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107233524/https://www.vice.com/en/article/rq8wd6/you-need-to-listen-to-weird-paul | url = https://www.vice.com/en/article/rq8wd6/you-need-to-listen-to-weird-paul | title = You Need To Listen To Weird Paul | dead-url = no | last = Ogiba | first = Jeff | work = [[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]] | date = 2012-09-04 | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-date = 2020-11-07}}</ref>其中16首曲目的标题都和专辑相同<ref>{{cite news | archive-date = 2020-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200719065815/https://www.post-gazette.com/uncategorized/2006/04/20/Adventures-of-Weird-Paul-Documentary-sheds-light-on-quirky-Pittsburgh-music-legend/stories/200604200363 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.post-gazette.com/uncategorized/2006/04/20/Adventures-of-Weird-Paul-Documentary-sheds-light-on-quirky-Pittsburgh-music-legend/stories/200604200363 | title = Adventures of Weird Paul: Documentary sheds light on quirky Pittsburgh music legend | last = Mervis | first = Scott | newspaper = [[匹兹堡邮报|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]] | date = 2006-04-20 | accessdate = 2020-12-13}}</ref>。

《神秘科学影院3000》（''{{lang|en|Mystery Science Theater 3000}}''）是美国电视喜剧剧集，讲述主角和两个机器人朋友参加科学实验，实验过程就是强迫他们观看烂片。1999年8月1日《恐怖食肉虫》入选该剧第十季倒数第二集，在[[Syfy|科幻频道]]播映。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/mystery-science-theater-3000/episodes/203329/ | title = Mystery Science Theater 3000 Season 10 Episode Guide | work = TV Guide | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190803035054/https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/mystery-science-theater-3000/episodes/203329 | archive-date = 2019-08-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="DVD">{{cite web | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190803035047/https://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/65514/mystery-science-theater-3000-the-turkey-day-collection-xxxi/ | title = Mystery Science Theater 3000: The Turkey Day Collection | last = Sinnott | dead-url = no | url = https://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/65514/mystery-science-theater-3000-the-turkey-day-collection-xxxi/ | first = John | work = DVD Talk | date = 2014-11-25 | archive-date = 2019-08-03}}</ref>一同播放的还有短片《[[弹簧狂热|弹簧狂热]]》（''{{lang|en|A Case of Spring Fever}}''）<ref name="DVD" />。2014年，呐喊工厂推出《神秘科学影院3000》剧集“火鸡节收藏”{{lang|en|DVD}}，收录的四集分别是《恐怖食肉虫》、《[[丛林女神|丛林女神]]》（''{{lang|en|Jungle Goddess}}''）、 《[[彩山|彩山]]》（''{{lang|en|The Painted Hills}}''）和《[[尖叫的头骨|尖叫的头骨]]》（''{{lang|en|The Screaming Skull}}''）<ref name="DVD" />。

